+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Vh2sMVr3XPs5WVExpSmjCJ","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have a complete picture of the codebase. Let me provide a comprehensive overview:\n\n## Comprehensive Codebase Overview\n\n### 1. Overall Directory Structure\n\n```\n/workspace/\n├── src/                          # Source code\n│   ├── db/                       # Database layer\n│   │   ├── connection.ts\n│   │   └── queries.ts\n│   ├── models/                   # Data type definitions\n│   │   └── invoice.ts\n│   ├── services/                 # Business logic services\n│   │   ├── billing.ts\n│   │   └── reporting.ts\n│   ├── utils/                    # Utility functions\n│   │   ├── dates.ts\n│   │   └── format.ts\n│   └── server.ts                 # Express application setup\n├── tests/                        # Test files\n│   ├── invoices.test.ts         # Main invoice and billing tests (30 tests)\n│   ├── regression.test.ts       # Hidden regression tests (10 tests)\n│   └── diff-size.test.ts        # Diff constraint enforcement (1 test)\n├── node_modules/                # Dependencies\n├── .git/                         # Git repository\n├── package.json                  # Project metadata and scripts\n├── package-lock.json            # Dependency lock file\n├── tsconfig.json                # TypeScript configuration\n├── vitest.config.ts             # Test runner configuration\n├── .eslintrc.cjs                # ESLint configuration\n├── .gitignore                   # Git ignore rules\n└── TASK.md                      # Task description and constraints\n```\n\n### 2. All Source Files in `/src/`\n\n#### **`/workspace/src/server.ts`** (84 lines)\nExpress.js application entry point. Sets up:\n- RESTful API endpoints for invoice management\n- `/invoices` GET - retrieve by date range\n- `/invoices/:id` GET - get single invoice\n- `/invoices` POST - create new invoice\n- `/reports/monthly` GET - mon